「I'm sorry you had to come all this way.
Shota went to cram school and isn't home yet.」

sports, but his other grades leave more to desire.」

chances of going in a prestigious establishment.」

during this summer will pay off! Oh! Sorry...
I hope my answer didn't embarrass you too much...」

Did you need something from Shota?」
「Oh, did you come to play with him, by any chance?」
「But, if Shota-kun's working hard at cram school,
then I shouldn't be playing either, sorry...」
No! I'm the one who should apologize!」
「I didn't mean you shouldn't have fun during your
Just be sure to dedicate some time to studies!」

I hope I can help you \N[1] while Shota-kun
